	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65140219"><p>One other difference is that before banging rocks together, we're usually expected to submit a formal paper discussing what we want to bang, how we want to bang it, what pieces we expect to see and why.</p><p>Oh, and the stones are much, much smaller although in terms of mass equivalence we're slowly getting to the size of a pebble.</p></div>
